snippet.title: 🎮 TankWars.io Development 🗺️ New Maps Sketches 🎨
snippet.description:
New TankWars .io maps concepts & crazy ideas we're considering for map themes.
► Play TankWars.io: http://tankwars.io/
WORK IN PROGRESS! Let us know what you think!

Try our unique 🎨 Map Editor 🎨 where you can create your own maps! http://designer.tankwars.io (BETA!)

▼ TankWars.io Videos
⚡ Scout Tank gameplay https://youtu.be/j-ZG9TVkko0
💪 Mammoth Tank gameplay https://youtu.be/4u9AbxcAW9Y
✔️ TankWars.io tanks gameplay https://youtu.be/dOw47w3CmGQ
👊 Tank STOMP Power-up https://youtu.be/dOw47w3CmGQ
🎮 Tank Teleport Power-up https://youtu.be/hNIoxU83SaI

▼Gamemodes
⚔️ Conquest
👑 KingDM (King DeathMatch)

... many more gamemodes coming soon!

▼ Follow us for more tank wars!
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/tankwarsio/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayOn_io
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/tankwars/
